<br>
 I think women (in general) are naturally more compassionate, nurturing, spiritual (and intelligent <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> )  And God gave the men the responsibility of the priesthood and leadership in the home(note leader not boss) to help make up for their lack in those other areas.<br>
